          "id": "Paragraph-7b13756f-4234-4c78-aacb-081a73a23789",
          "size": "xl",
          "text": "Back in 2014, a small group of hosts asked a simple question: Why is running a holiday rental so complicated? Booking calendars overlapped, prices never kept up with demand, and valuable hours vanished in spreadsheets. We decided to fix that.\n",
          "color": "#545454",
          "weight": "normal",
