          "size": "xl",
          "text": "Since then, MyAllocator has grown from a kitchen-table idea into a global platform trusted by thousands of property owners and managers. From single-apartment Airbnb hosts to multi-property vacation-rental agencies, we empower every customer with enterprise-level technology, without the enterprise price tag.\n",
          "color": "#545454",
